item.title: Port Forwarding help!
item.dc:creator: @r0ckstar96 r0ckstar96
item.description:
@r0ckstar96 wrote:

easy way:
download uTorrent
Open it up
Go to Options > Preferences > Connection
Change port to 43594
Click apply then click ok
now you’ve portforwarded!
